      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That makes sense. When you mention the \"supposed progression,\" do you mean that the transition from those primitive structures to modern civilization is basically just a move toward Western-style organization? Like, is the standard \"civilized\" model inherently based on European or Western development?",
